name: Alex Kelly
values: Compassion, personal growth, community service, and maintaining a balanced life.

summary: Alex Kelly is a 28-year-old, non-binary, Spanish and English speaking registered nurse from Seattle, Washington. They currently live in Los Angeles, California, where they are ready to meet a potential life partner. Politically liberal and agnostic by religion, they hold values such as compassion, personal growth, community service, and maintaining a balanced life in high regard. In their free time, they enjoy traveling, hiking, yoga, reading, and participating in charity runs. They identify as Gay and are interested in monogamy. Although they currently do not have children, they would like to have them in the future. They own a dog and lead an active lifestyle. They occasionally drink, but do not smoke or use marijuana or other drugs. Their match preferences feature a partner aged 25-35 years, who has an active lifestyle, doesn't smoke, drinks occasionally, and shares the desire to have children in the future.
